  "texts": [
    "These newly formed words are then joined using an underscore character (\"_\").",
    "(e.g., subject-\"môn ho. c\" becomes \"môn_ho.",
    "c\", course-\"khóa ho.",
    "c\" becomes \"khóa_ho.",
    "c\").Furthermore, to comply with dataset privacy policies, we implemented a text anonymization tool to censor any personally identifiable information (PII) within the sentences."
  ],
